Granola crusted french toast, Granola crusted french toast, Granola crusted french toast, Granola crusted french toast, Granola crusted french toast... ...I was hoping that maybe if I said it 5 times, it would suddenly appear like Candyman. Along with a big veg & egg or the goat cheese and sundried tomato scramble, and I'm good to go for the rest of the day. Eat here at your own risk. That brunch, it haunts my dreams.
